    <item>
      <title>美联储对抵押贷款的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/the-fed-s-impact-on-mortgages-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国现有房屋销售数据在 11 月跃升至八个月高点，因为购房者开始勉强接受超过 6% 的抵押贷款利率。Dynex Capital 联席首席执行官、总裁兼首席投资官 Smriti Popenoe 参加了彭博公开利息，讨论未来一年房地产市场的前景。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/the-fed-s-impact-on-mortgages-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 16:01:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织与阿根廷就 440 亿美元贷款协议进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/imf-in-talks-with-argentina-on-loan-to-succeed-44-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷正在与国际货币基金组织寻求一项新计划，以接替其目前达成的 440 亿美元协议，这是朝着解决华盛顿贷款机构最棘手的协议之一迈出的一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/imf-in-talks-with-argentina-on-loan-to-succeed-44-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 16:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路易吉·曼吉奥内被引渡至纽约接受谋杀指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/luigi-mangione-extradited-to-ny-to-face-murder-charges-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼哈顿中城枪杀联合健康集团高管的嫌疑人路易吉·曼吉奥内 (Luigi Mangione) 周四在法庭上放弃了反对此举的立场，随后被引渡到纽约接受谋杀指控。12 月 19 日，曼吉奥内走出宾夕法尼亚州霍利迪斯堡的布莱尔县法院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/luigi-mangione-extradited-to-ny-to-face-murder-charges-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:53:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息后，美国收益率曲线创 2022 年以来最陡峭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/us-yield-curve-is-steepest-since-2022-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[较长期美国国债周四走弱，推动收益率曲线趋陡至 30 个月前的水平，此前美联储采取了强硬的利率放松政策，并预计明年降息次数将减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/us-yield-curve-is-steepest-since-2022-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:27:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克暂停降息但仍为进一步宽松政策敞开大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/czechs-hold-rates-after-eight-cuts-on-persistent-inflation-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克央行暂停了长达一年的货币宽松周期，为最早在2月份重启降息留下了空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/czechs-hold-rates-after-eight-cuts-on-persistent-inflation-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 13:30:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西斥资创纪录 80 亿美元遏制卢拉引发的市场崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/brazil-market-rout-risks-a-crisis-as-lula-resists-austerity-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着巴西货币暴跌，该国市场多年来首次成为国际关注的焦点，总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦的高级经济助理们面临着严峻的现实。他们担心，自己无力阻止恐慌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/brazil-market-rout-risks-a-crisis-as-lula-resists-austerity-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Archegos 法官拒绝 Bill Hwang 减刑申请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/bill-hwang-returning-to-court-to-fight-for-less-prison-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官确认了对 Archegos Capital Management 创始人 Bill Hwang 18 年监禁的判决，驳回了有关他应该被允许在家中舒适地度过三分之一刑期的论点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/bill-hwang-returning-to-court-to-fight-for-less-prison-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强给出口前景蒙上阴影，美国小麦延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/wheat-set-for-longest-run-of-losses-since-june-on-supply-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强和对供应过剩的担忧导致芝加哥小麦价格连续第六个交易日走低，小麦价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/wheat-set-for-longest-run-of-losses-since-june-on-supply-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 06:58:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员重新评估美联储路径，股市反弹乏力：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，美国股市反弹势头减弱，因交易员们在考虑美联储的政策走向和经济数据。日本央行维持借贷成本不变后，日元继续走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 22:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
